<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Perfil Criado! - PetLove</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #FF69B4;
            --secondary-color: #FFB6C1;
            --background-color: #FFF5F7;
            --text-color: #333;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .success-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .success-header h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .success-header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .qr-section {
            margin: 3rem 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: var(--background-color);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .qr-code {
            max-width: 200px;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        }

        .qr-code img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .photos-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .photo-item {
            position: relative;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .photo-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .photo-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.3);
        }

        .button.secondary {
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
        }

        .floating-emojis {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .emoji {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 2rem;
            animation: float-up 4s ease-in-out infinite;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        @keyframes float-up {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg);
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-100px) rotate(360deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .success-header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .button-group {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .button {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="floating-emojis" id="emojis"></div>

    <div class="container animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
        <div class="success-header">
            <span style="font-size: 4em;">ðŸŽ‰</span>
            <h1>Perfil Criado com Sucesso!</h1>
            <p>O perfil de <%= nomePet %> estÃ¡ pronto para ser compartilhado</p>
        </div>

        <div class="qr-section animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
            <h2>QR Code do Perfil</h2>
            <p>Escaneie para acessar o perfil do <%= nomePet %></p>
            <div class="qr-code">
                <img src="<%= qrCode %>" alt="QR Code do perfil">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="photos-grid">
            <% fotos.forEach((foto, index) => { %>
                <div class="photo-item animate__animated animate__fadeIn" style="animation-delay: <%= index * 0.2 %>s;">
                    <img src="<%= foto %>" alt="Foto de <%= nomePet %>">
                </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="/pet/<%= petId %>" class="button">Ver Perfil</a>
            <a href="/" class="button secondary">Voltar para InÃ­cio</a>
        </div>
    </div>

